Welcome to One Click Installer, with this you can setup site in matter of minutes. Some Points to note, make sure this is a fresh installation and while installer is running please do not refresh the page. A notification will show after demo has been installed.

Very important: be sure to run the installer only once! And be sure to run the installer only on a new empty website, as running it on existing websites can rewrite (delete) pre existing contents and change settings! Demo content cannot be installed in websites with pre-esisting contents or your website can be overwritten!

Please also be sure, in case of problems, that your PHP max execution time is at least 60 seconds. In case of problems with the demo contents installation, you need to ask a suggestion to your hosting provider in order to increase your PHP upload and execution limits, and be sure that CURL is enabled.
